OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784114300
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cpresumed dead after kayak capsize
OL,6,FThe family of a 19-year-old kayaker
OL,7,Fwho is missing presumed dead off
OL,8,FNorthumberland have paid tribute to a
OL,9,F"much-loved son, brother, grandson,
OL,10,Fnephew, team-mate and friend".
OL,12,FMichael Henry, from the Rothbury area,
OL,13,Fwas one of two men on a kayak near
OL,14,FBoulmer when it capsized on the
OL,15,Fevening of 7 July, Northumbria Police
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FThe other man managed to make it to a
OL,19,Fbuoy and was rescued by the coastguard.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@]O]
