OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784114300
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cpresumed dead after kayak capsize
OL,6,FExtensive searches for Mr Henry were
OL,7,Fconducted in the sea but Northumbria
OL,8,FPolice said on Wednesday (15 July) the
OL,9,Foperation has now concluded and they
OL,10,Frepeated their belief the teenager has
OL,11,Fdied.
OL,13,FMr Henry's family said in a statement:
OL,14,F"We would like to thank everyone for
OL,15,Fall their love, kindness and support
OL,16,Fnow and throughout Michael's life; it
OL,17,Fwas that love and kindness that made
OL,18,Fhim the marvellous person he was.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784114300
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cpresumed dead after kayak capsize
OL,6,F"Michael was a much-loved son,
OL,7,Fbrother, grandson, nephew, team-mate
OL,8,Fand friend; a keen sportsman who loved
OL,9,Fthe outdoors.
OL,11,F"Michael was preparing to go
OL,12,Ftravelling this summer and hoping to
OL,13,Fstart university next academic year.
OL,14,FMichael will be forever in our
OL,15,Fthoughts, and we will miss him.
OL,17,F"Our thanks go to the emergency
OL,18,Fservices and everyone who is helping
OL,19,Fto search for Michael."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784114300
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cpresumed dead after kayak capsize
OL,6,FChief Inspector Jon Caisley said:
OL,7,F"This is a tragic update to share, and
OL,8,FI would like to extend our deepest
OL,9,Fsympathies to Michael's family and
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,F"Despite extensive searches at sea and
OL,13,Fon the coast, we have been unable to
OL,14,Ffind Michael and he is sadly believed
OL,15,Fto have died at sea.
OL,17,F"We know the impact this news will
OL,18,Fhave upon his loved ones and the wider
OL,19,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784114300
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cpresumed dead after kayak capsize
OL,6,FMr Caisley added: "I would also like
OL,7,Fto thank all of our officers and
OL,8,Fpartners for their assistance in the
OL,9,Fsearch efforts to find Michael.
OL,11,F"We would continue to ask that people
OL,12,Frespect the family's privacy at this
OL,13,Ftime."
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@AOUuD@FO]
